text: Kochel am See (Bavarian: Koche am Sää) is a municipality and a town in Bad Tölz-Wolfratshausen, a district (Landkreis) in Upper Bavaria, on the shores of Kochelsee. The municipality consists of the districts Altjoch, Brunnenbach, Ort, Pessenbach, Pfisterberg, Walchensee and Ried. == References == == Other websites == * Kochel Homepage Category:Towns in Bavaria
